{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840266749,"sessionID":"ses_287aeab4bffeo8y7CyfDhiqNUm","part":{"id":"prt_d78540889001Qt8qS3PfWNJU2f","messageID":"msg_d7851e663001u41Hx4VgfG9P4o","sessionID":"ses_287aeab4bffeo8y7CyfDhiqNUm","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-c853f3489d6f4028b590ec5aecdad66f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# CodeInterpreter CRD Type Definition Design\n\n## AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n\n**Module**: `pkg/apis`  \n**Language**: Go  \n**Size**: S  \n**Purpose**: Define Kubernetes CRD type definitions for CodeInterpreter resources, enable client-go code generation, and provide type-safe API access for code execution environment management.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Package Structure\n\n```\npkg/apis/\n└── runtime/\n    └── v1alpha1/\n        ├── types.go                   # Core type definitions (AgentRuntime + Sandbox types)\n        ├── register.go                # Scheme registration\n        ├── doc.go                     # Package documentation\n        ├── deepcopy.go                # DeepCopy methods (generated)\n        └── types_test.go              # Unit tests\n```\n\n### API Group\n\n- **Group**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- **Version**: `v1alpha1`\n- **Scope**: `Namespaced`\n- **Kind**: `CodeInterpreter`\n- **Resource Plural**: `codeinterpreters`\n- **Short Names**: `ci`\n\n### Component Interactions\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                     Kubernetes API Server                   │\n│                                                             │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │       runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1          │  │\n│  │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │  │\n│  │  │  codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh │  │  │\n│  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │  │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                           │\n                           │ k8s client-go\n                           ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                  client-go (Generated)                     │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │  clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/         │  │\n│  │    • CodeInterpreterInterface                        │  │\n│  │    • REST CRUD + Watch                               │  │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │  informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/        │  │\n│  │    • CodeInterpreterInformer                         │  │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │  listers/runtime/v1alpha1/                          │  │\n│  │    • CodeInterpreterLister                           │  │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                           │\n                           │ Controllers\n                           ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                   Code Execution Components                 │\n│  ┌─────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐ │\n│  │  PicoD Daemon   │  │  Session Store  │  │  Router     │ │\n│  │  (per pod)      │  │  (Redis)        │  │  (Nginx)    │ │\n│  └─────────────────┘  └─────────────────┘  └─────────────┘ │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### CodeInterpreter\n\n**File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n\n```go\n// +genclient\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +k8s:openapi-gen=true\n// +kubebuilder:resource:shortName=ci;codeinterpreter\n// +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Ready\",type=\"boolean\",JSONPath=\".status.ready\"\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Runtime\",type=\"string\",JSONPath=\".spec.runtime\"\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n\n// CodeInterpreter defines a custom resource for managing code execution environments.\n// It represents a code interpreter sandbox that executes user code in a secure environment.\ntype CodeInterpreter struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n\n    Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec,omitempty\"`\n    Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n}\n\n// CodeInterpreterSpec defines the desired state of a CodeInterpreter.\ntype CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n    // Image is the container image for the interpreter (e.g., \"python:3.11-slim\").\n    // +required\n    Image string `json:\"image\"`\n\n    // Runtime specifies the execution environment type.\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"python\"\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=python;javascript;typescript;go\n    // +optional\n    Runtime string `json:\"runtime,omitempty\"`\n\n    // Timeout defines the maximum execution time for code snippets.\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"5m\"\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Type=string\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Format=duration\n    // +optional\n    Timeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"timeout,omitempty\"`\n\n    // Resources defines compute resource requirements for the interpreter container.\n    // +optional\n    Resources *SandboxContainerResources `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n\n    // Env defines environment variables to inject into the interpreter container.\n    // +optional\n    Env []SandboxEnvVar `json:\"env,omitempty\"`\n\n    // EnabledPackages specifies allowed packages for the interpreter.\n    // Only packages listed here can be imported/required. Empty list allows all.\n    // +optional\n    EnabledPackages []string `json:\"enabledPackages,omitempty\"`\n}\n\n// CodeInterpreterStatus defines the observed state of a CodeInterpreter.\ntype CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n    // Ready indicates whether the interpreter is ready to execute code.\n    // +optional\n    Ready bool `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n\n    // Conditions represent the latest available observations of the CodeInterpreter's current state.\n    // +optional\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n\n    // ObservedGeneration is the most recent generation observed by the controller.\n    // +optional\n    ObservedGeneration int64 `json:\"observedGeneration,omitempty\"`\n}\n\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n\n// CodeInterpreterList contains a list of CodeInterpreter objects.\ntype CodeInterpreterList struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n\n    Items []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n}\n```\n\n### SandboxContainerResources (Reused from AgentRuntime)\n\n```go\n// SandboxContainerResources defines resource requirements for a container.\ntype SandboxContainerResources struct {\n    // Limits defines the resource limits.\n    // +optional\n    Limits SandboxResourceList `json:\"limits,omitempty\"`\n\n    // Requests defines the resource requests.\n    // +optional\n    Requests SandboxResourceList `json:\"requests,omitempty\"`\n}\n\n// SandboxResourceList defines a list of resources.\ntype SandboxResourceList struct {\n    // CPU defines CPU resources.\n    // +optional\n    CPU string `json:\"cpu,omitempty\"`\n\n    // Memory defines memory resources.\n    // +optional\n    Memory string `json:\"memory,omitempty\"`\n\n    // EphemeralStorage defines ephemeral storage resources.\n    // +optional\n    EphemeralStorage string `json:\"ephemeralStorage,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n### SandboxEnvVar (Reused from AgentRuntime)\n\n```go\n// SandboxEnvV